{"tid":1628262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前線必須停！勇武方式已行唔通！只會弄巧反拙！","createTime":"2019-10-06T01:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T02:23:17.000Z","uid":11809,"like":6,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"82c5f9cec8c5f73c99f3ff89ba12acdffa8a16bf","tid":1628262,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jiZE2sm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjiZE2sm.jpg&h=1da72e63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n［朋友叫我幫手post]<br />\n<br />\n勇武派，好多謝你地過去幾個月的奉獻和犧牲，保護這場運動，保護運動中的和理非。<br />\n<br />\n我作為一個和理非，而家懇求你地停止勇武行為。打砸搶商鋪，放火，私了，起底 這些行為，一你做嘅果一刻，覺得好爽，覺得出左啖氣。但係，你覺得咁樣做，真係幫到場運動推向大家想要的目標咩？？<br />\n<br />\n林鄭不斷設局，故意激怒大家，故意引勇武派升級暴力行為，就比政府有更多的口實立尼個法，立果個法，甚至走向一國一制。<br />\n<br />\n我支持罷買，罷食，罷搭，推美國制裁香港高官警察，推美國人權法，繼續爭取國際支持。這些才是有效的方式。<br />\n<br />\n暴力從來都不能帶來成果！<br />\n勇武派，醒啦！停啦！<br />\n<br />\n而且，大家都覺得很多黑警混入示威者，做很多暴力行為。那怎麼解決？最有效的方法就係我地自己人停止這些暴力行為，(暫時)變成和理非，由得d黑警自己玩，睇佢地自己表演！然後全體和理非堅持每個週末都集會遊行，要求成立獨立調查委員會調查整件事件！<br />\n<br />\n我認為，訴求要集中焦點到&rdquo;獨立調查委員會&rdquo;。之後，係成立左獨立調查委員會之後再去要求其他訴求，才會有可能實現。<br />\n<br />\n肯定又有人話我咁做係&rdquo;割蓆&rdquo;。我認為尼d唔係割蓆，而係be water的體現：勇武派暫變合理非，繼續行。<br />\n<br />\n電影Green Book裡面有一句話，送給大家：<br />\nYou never win with violence. You only win when you maintain your dignity. Dignity always prevails.<del></del>"},{"pid":"8ded049d1677bf7460ddea8432ea97608ea8d339","tid":1628262,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:55:40.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"57b55b980aea53426e504ea457b3da1f119d8917","tid":1628262,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:55:53.000Z","msg":"推 2/10"},{"pid":"a32dba390bb9bcb70de7aa45e5846a15933acf83","tid":1628262,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:56:26.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"765d6c454bab6bc0e60c344f9580e937ae69a665","tid":1628262,"uid":116511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:56:39.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"bb074c627463e4b05be33e9505d17afc4f2eef63","tid":1628262,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:57:01.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"f28e9c339dc07ef68a7dd9c34b6b94528d3daaa8","tid":1628262,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:57:20.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"d36f04750e8e848a8893fe71e51f7996067a7b0a","tid":1628262,"uid":277589,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:57:29.000Z","msg":"邊個最怕勇武派？"},{"pid":"08f3ebd547ce7bbacc5059e66c7c93480d60ee89","tid":1628262,"uid":15055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:57:37.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 證明方向正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4a4110200c39e2b3f8d8bfbb27be11507e30dc","tid":1628262,"uid":106798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:59:16.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"af1d5e3f2db9dcd61e85c0a462e6cf3f74691e20","tid":1628262,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:00:22.000Z","msg":"風向好明顯，就係唔再發動大規模公民抗命，轉為發動快閃式裝修行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628251</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5e1782822ab843334bc7a436e88dff16fee7bc0c","tid":1628262,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:02:25.000Z","msg":"6/0"},{"pid":"09a28728b8aeb71a363c3243f55c243e2e7411e2","tid":1628262,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:03:21.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"3b5e3312b50833334783d38ed89287e0e162de57","tid":1628262,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:03:45.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"0adfa6dc7ba3972391df76729aafc9646abe623d","tid":1628262,"uid":267823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:03:56.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"32071ea61c093b2a5947658c58d50caffd8957de","tid":1628262,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:03:58.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"29e2f7919bd49c526f36259742b44a2556c13f70","tid":1628262,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:04:24.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"ee5fa87804034eb5a84e6a9bc98a38673b6eb25f","tid":1628262,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:05:29.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"006ff8341ccfda442f177a52aae5de24df9011ea","tid":1628262,"uid":6840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:06:24.000Z","msg":"講真獨立調查後會點？ 真係會有人出黎負責？ 可以懲誡警隊？"},{"pid":"24183df838dcd6431b2ee6e89c1bb00975fb6a7b","tid":1628262,"uid":28558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:07:00.000Z","msg":"今日吹風<br />\n<br />\n和勇割蓆<br />\n<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"62b1103c750c7ee4aca08fc923ac7ea57ba8f92a","tid":1628262,"uid":245537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:07:06.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係 兄弟爬山 各自努力"},{"pid":"842b02a3039028995dbbcb8c746cac1d3d8662c5","tid":1628262,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:08:38.000Z","msg":"冇睇哂，但邊有士威者搶，咪亂屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec8c90191877568cdc6e0969b7a8ec2351e84f7","tid":1628262,"uid":1181,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:09:31.000Z","msg":"罷買罷食罷搭已經做咗兩個月 想請問有咩咁顯著既成果？<br />\n有兩個學生俾人用真槍射、起馬七個人眼部受傷、數唔盡既手足身體受到不同程度既傷害，國際關注我地一直做緊，你自問有無真係做過野幫手足？班廢老拎刀拎棍打人個時你係邊？你依加叫我地唔好獅鳥要和平？忽撚咗？<br />\n<br />\n仲有，你句「勇武派，醒啦！停啦！」真係特撚別銀耳，屌你老母講到自己最撚醒智者咁既款，手足俾人打個時你咪又係係屋企涼冷氣叫人散水"},{"pid":"db6201b95a3765c50933afa467e8f7ffa64d5c70","tid":1628262,"uid":78513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:14:54.000Z","msg":"啱！<br />\n我地應該打不還手罵不還口<br />\n咁我地就得到全世界口頭支持"},{"pid":"e29ef446a10751d0f5208e1df6500a20d93c2360","tid":1628262,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:15:36.000Z","msg":"跟林鄭一齊割"}]}